quran[11{c,v,t}:
21,25,"hum ne tum se pehlay jo rasool bhi bheja hai uss ko yahi wahi ki hai ke mere siwa koi khuda nahi hai, pas tum log meri hi bandagi karo"
21,26,"yeh kehte hain"" Rehman aulaad rakhta hai"" subhan Allah , woh to bande hain jinhein azzt di gayi hai"
21,27,uss ke huzoor barh kar nahi boltay aur bas uss ke hukum par amal karte hain
21,28,"jo kuch unn ke samnay hai usay bhi woh jaanta hai aur jo kuch unn se oojhal hai is se bhi woh bakhabar hai woh kisi ki sifarish nahi karte bajuz uss ke jis ke haq mein sifarish suneney par Allah raazi ho, aur woh is ke khauf se daray rehtay hain"
21,29,"aur jo unn mein se koi keh day ke Allah ke siwa mein bhi aik khuda hon, to usay hum Jahannum ki saza den, hamaray haan zaalmon ka yahi badla hai"
21,30,"kya woh log jinhon ne ( NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki baat maan-ne se ) inkaar kar diya hai ghhor nahi karte ke yeh sab aasman aur zameen baahum miley hue thay, phir hum ne aِnhin judda kya, aur pani se har zindah cheez peda ki kya woh ( hamari is khalaqi ko ) nahi mantay ?"
21,31,"aur hum ne zameen mein pahar jama diye taakay woh inhen le kar dhalak nah jaye aur is mein kushadah rahein bana den, shayad ke log apna rasta maloom kar len"
21,32,"aur hum ne aasman ko aik mehfooz chhat bana diya, magar yeh hain ke is ki nishanion ki taraf tojj_h hi nahi karte"
21,33,aur woh Allah hi hai jis ne raat aur din banaye aur sooraj aur chaand ko peda kya sab aik aik fallak mein teer rahay hain
21,34,"aur ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hameshgi to hum ne tum se pehlay bhi kisi ensaan ke liye nahi rakhi hai agar tum mar gay to kya yeh log hamesha jeetay rahen ge ?"
21,35,"har jandaar ko mout ka maza chakhna hai, aur hum achay aur buray halaat mein daal kar tum sab ki azmaish kar rahay hain aakhir kaar tumhe hamari hi taraf palatna hai"
